With Californium, we can provide mature transport layer for
coap
,
coaps
but also more experimental transport layer like
coap+tcp
,
coaps+tcp
and
OSCORE
.

Maybe it could be better to seperate all this transport layer in different modules to have clear dependencies and so user only pick-up transport layer he needs and so didn't embedded undesired dependencies.
